38:12.360 --> 38:17.400
Then his son came, touched
his hand and he lived on.

38:19.960 --> 38:21.120
Is that your excuse?

38:23.760 --> 38:24.720
I'm not sorry.

38:26.240 --> 38:27.440
You will have to fire me.

38:27.960 --> 38:29.560
Yeah, I might do that.

38:35.480 --> 38:36.440
Tomorrow.

38:37.120 --> 38:38.240
I'll fire you there.

38:47.120 --> 38:49.680
Incredible that you
hijacked a helicopter today.

38:49.840 --> 38:53.440
Please, you've already hijacked
emergency vans for a taco.

38:53.560 --> 38:55.520
You were there,
don't you remember?

38:55.640 --> 38:58.480
No, I don't even remember that.

38:59.920 --> 39:04.080
Not looking, two nervous
interns at two o'clock.

39:12.880 --> 39:16.320
Want to know who I
picked for the Waverly job?

39:16.600 --> 39:18.160
-For us everything is okay.
-No matter how.

39:19.240 --> 39:20.080
Good.

39:24.600 --> 39:26.120
Because I've already
made my decision.

39:42.600 --> 39:45.720
Team doctor
assistant Dr.  Noa Kean
